		&lt;h1&gt;Artificial Intelligence&lt;/h1&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;
			I'm interested in AI because of I believe in its power and potential to transform industries and 
			advance humanity. AI software and hardware are much more meaningful than social media, video 
			streaming and other purely digital products and services. It will become the new engine of economies
			and societies.
			&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
			I'm interested in learning AI technology and applying it to solve issues both in business and science
			worlds. I hope by launching the Artificial Intelligence Programme, I will be able to systematically 
			and methodically acquire AI knowledge and skills and share my progress with the public.
			&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
