		&lt;h1&gt;Web Development&lt;/h1&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;
			In the foreseeable future, the Internet will continue to be the primary platform through which 
			people search for information and acquire knowledge. As the Internet evolves, it has become 
			more powerful, useful and impactful.
			&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
			I developed a passion for web development since taking that web-based applications course in school.
			I still find designing and building feature-rich, visually appealing websites an enjoyable experience.
			I love building products that people are willing to use to meed their changing demands.
			&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
			Following the introduction of Web3, this space is now more exciting than ever before. I'm keen to 
			acquire knowledge and skills in web development. This Programme will help me acquire web technologies
			such as HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript, etc.
